{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f5ada1e5-23cf-4716-b903-8b834ff5f36f", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f5ada1e5-23cf-4716-b903-8b834ff5f36f@1.pkg/1772597679741/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597679953", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f5ada1e5-23cf-4716-b903-8b834ff5f36f@1.pkg/1772597679741/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597679953"}, "identifier": "f5ada1e5-23cf-4716-b903-8b834ff5f36f", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查掌握科学规划生活的方法。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①：李某找到了自己的奋斗坐标启示青少年要制定明确目标，并兼顾现实需要。因此①正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>②：在在初中阶段的学习中，我们要合理规划时间，协调短期任务与长期成长。因此②正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>③：&ldquo;照搬学习方法&rdquo;做法错误，我们可以借鉴他人学习方法，但不能照搬。因此③错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>④：&ldquo;依赖家长监督，有人督促才完成学习计划&rdquo;做法不当，且与材料无关。因此④错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>①②正确，因此选A</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）随着乡村文旅产业的蓬勃发展，李某大学毕业后选择回到家乡做一名民宿管家。她凭借专业优势向游客提供旅游咨询、活动策划等服务，不仅为游客带来美好体验，而且找到了自己的奋斗坐标。这启示我们在初中阶段的学习中要（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①制定明确目标，兼顾学科基础与兴趣发展</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②合理规划时间，协调短期任务与长期成长</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③借鉴他人经验，照搬学习方法来提升成绩</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>④依赖家长监督，有人督促才完成学习计划</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）随着乡村文旅产业的蓬勃发展，李某大学毕业后选择回到家乡做一名民宿管家。她凭借专业优势向游客提供旅游咨询、活动策划等服务，不仅为游客带来美好体验，而且找到了自己的奋斗坐标。这启示我们在初中阶段的学习中要（    ）①制定明确目标，兼顾学科基础与兴趣发展②合理规划时间，协调短期任务与长期成长③借鉴他人经验，照搬学习方法来提升成绩④依赖家长监督，有人督促才完成学习计划", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f5ada1e5-23cf-4716-b903-8b834ff5f36f@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977876252", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①②</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>①④</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>②③</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>③④</span></p><